channel.description:
Hello i am James/EvolutionJB,
I played private servers for several years (2-3), i spent a certain amount of time coding, hosting and released a server once although it wasn't of great standard. After two years of Official Runescape (I currently have 4 accounts but that's not really improtant at the moment)
Basicly i have done my GCSE in Business and passed with an A*; i am going straight into business and i am starting off here and i will eventually expand. I will guarantee a certain time i will stay with you for.
I am looking for a Running server which could benifit from my help. I will help in many ways such as...
- Cheapest, most Effective way to spend your budget (If you have chosen to have one) - Keep track of your Costs and profits and calculate certain calculations - Advertisement - Make [b]money[/b]! ... and more
If you are intrested contact me... Jamesbarker123@hotmail.co.uk - We will disscuss further if you like by msn please don't leave questions on this Topic.
